{"h78d96130g2ecbg4649gbeb1gf7a6c421218e": ["<i>Take a closer look the ball.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "510b8122-d8bc-4ba9-a8d0-348d19b272e4"], "h957aeff9g5330g4ef7g8e6bg1394860ff7e8": ["*The ball is well-chewed and still moist with drool - Scratch has been playing with it recently.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "a9b861fe-593f-7141-31af-ced9d49d05ae"], "hc410009cg9989g4551g8c71g509975f762d8": ["<i>Call out for Scratch.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "b4105949-7e5b-4247-a314-f1984a361cd2"], "h73ba9e28g839cg450dgb5ccg04648be785d1": ["*You listen intently - nothing. It occurs to you that the owlbear cub is nowhere to be seen either...*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "9a260899-8a4b-55d0-e81b-f9e02a8cdc2a"], "h21643b1eg8398g4736gafeagea6873ff720b": ["<i>Whistle for Scratch.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "a4730f0b-e087-aa1b-7403-f12c33126fa7"], "h2752f13fg76eag45c8ga50ag7907c47ed571": ["*Nothing. Only the still of the night.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "d268c959-a949-dab6-ecb3-bf98f64e6d5f"], "h6ed5330fg8c82g4dfeg9dbeg8151a4d3c502": ["<i>Hurry towards the sound.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "be296320-1627-3b6c-3936-b71c462c82a2"], "hf3747fd1g00a9g48f4g935eg0585039308de": ["What's going on? I thought something was wrong.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "3d9cf72c-77ab-ea64-fedd-1cb0814a1e41"], "ha238fd43gc7bfg4a39ga77fg66f40645288a": ["Just a bad dream. It's all right.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "4dc89316-0b6a-ed62-ff26-54c93f10361f"], "hc18b1629g3322g4a2fg8a9dg94f2867da399": ["Goblins had me in a cage. Poked me with pointy sticks..", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "2619ccbc-a874-9833-6373-b090161796d9"], "hace407deg80a8g48b0g9231ge25af965e488": ["Hush now, it was just a nightmare. We're safe here, with master.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "f3d4241f-b06a-5e65-aaf3-dd9b3a60a279"], "hd77ca24bg63f0g4cd1gb534gba7928b53b11": ["Hush now, it was just a nightmare. We're safe here, with mistress.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "f3d4241f-b06a-5e65-aaf3-dd9b3a60a279"], "h22cc86b0g3382g41dcg8b4dgb9c722e8f5d8": ["Hush now, it was just a nightmare. We're safe here, with our guardian.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "f3d4241f-b06a-5e65-aaf3-dd9b3a60a279"], "h250dd163g26b3g40e6g9b1bge7fc57f308c2": ["He'll settle in. Give it a little time.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "f6b5c6b8-e915-7225-1f75-1cc9cd0ff34c"], "hd35b5d26g0386g452dg9102g2e1015dd17c0": ["You two looked cozy together. Bad dreams aside.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "1e7fbceb-bc27-32d6-eeb4-7a42da57385a"], "hcfbc2f4dgb54ag4e37ga3a9g25345ab16e6c": ["He's still young. I remember Gomwick would let me sleep under his cloak when I was a pup. It helps.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "174f60f2-bdbd-e88f-7fb3-787aab53e1af"], "h96845996gfdd4g40c7g925fg94fcb0fab6b7": ["All right then, so long as nobody's getting hurt.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "ad55edd8-dfe3-3c1b-9325-0469079abc6f"], "h84d0a3d6g580ag4e30g8cbeg735e7ee0d615": ["No hurt Scratch! Never!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "07e5ed27-3cad-da1d-5e1f-f679203e9f5b"], "hf2dec931ga0f1g4460gabafg42a341fb7a19": ["Easy now. The guardian's just looking out for us.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "348b3836-6a1b-3b82-0eab-53bb63d713c7"], "hd9ec6736g901dg417ag8d7bg717cab89ee41": ["Did you call me master just now...?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "0d6f931c-383d-e730-8fce-784265581f36"], "h3444eae9gb8e7g4c26gbfd5ge647c9813f69": ["Did you call me mistress just now...?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "0d6f931c-383d-e730-8fce-784265581f36"], "h5ff20e08g72a8g46degad4cgd9fc6daa98a5": ["Did you call me guardian just now...?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "0d6f931c-383d-e730-8fce-784265581f36"], "hdb24a57bg3507g4495gb8a3g6e5793831e5c": ["I... I suppose I did. You've been good to us - to both of us. Gomwick would be happy I'm with you, I think.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "8dae68a5-9cbf-b880-0b66-b0897ca97e26"], "h0fa17157gbdb2g4e97ga058g4867fbd4b083": ["Like it here. Warm fire, Scratch reminds me of big brother.", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "2aafc72c-0120-8a0c-5b5f-92a499837385"], "h90765508g5a01g4727gb505g8d6b91884954": ["Well, you're both welcome here.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "9862e9c7-e470-91b8-078b-f674c5fdee3e"], "h3585e748g9089g4202g808bgfefcf235fe91": ["Thank you. ", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "aaa9091d-03ea-6bf3-8abd-95541a364f2b"], "hf45b9fb1ge25fg4f4dg9471g1b4d55f2c8c9": ["Wait - did you say you have a brother?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "7d8fa40a-d212-7ad8-bab3-f77df6a5740e"], "h16213f01ged76g45b3gbeaagba6ce9858a09": ["Used to. Mother ate him.", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "9485aa1c-3a94-3bf9-4af5-26be53afc9b5"], "h885999c8gd5a4g4a1fg83e9gbcbc43203691": ["All right, keep it down. Folk are trying to rest.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "f9eb0742-0d61-d802-72cd-2b26a44d2cd9"], "hd0f3c2c1g36f8g4494gada3g60cc5bfbcd47": ["We will!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "f1eed433-4ffd-2056-52e9-d716047231a6"], "hb481f64agb023g407egb591ge614c4664304": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "b429155e-5f68-de22-7249-067a3b5669cb"], "h87a99ecdg914bg4e8fgace3g11df51f8d538": ["Best friends! It's nice to have company, while you're gone all day. ", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "6c5b1a1c-1b90-5055-6f49-f3a0c417c4ee"], "hc35de236g5ae9g4b44g9d27g735f63bac125": ["Are you two... friends?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "6cd0614c-ff82-43cd-2c28-1c16f79cb8a9"], "h378cf267gaad4g4befgb824gfac366d78e52": ["<i>Call to them.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "2076d49f-bac6-b2b0-bb53-22e4eceaeea6"], "hf1ffbdb7g08c1g42eegb52ag9e086d39c8d1": ["*Bark!*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "13910323-a430-4c4d-0340-dc381ca8c670"], "h1b929011ga77ag42a5gafd3g4ba708b45f12": ["<i>Pet Scratch.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "43005282-f598-ba16-5e49-4bc0d937e70f"], "hf3706495g4f32g431bg8524g0c7414d8aef2": ["<i>Pet Scratch.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "13e19f3e-ac8b-73d3-e27d-4b426a82fcc6"], "h7787580eg2170g45dfg8dc2g178f811f783f": ["<i>Pet the owlbear cub.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "ff989d75-bbf9-5786-f9d9-532f0d18f0d8"], "h74ef8297gc1f2g4d1eg8859g1007a8af77c1": ["<i>Pet the owlbear cub.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "bc848558-5f8a-3ffe-c55a-c9543d3aa939"], "h5877a3b4g59e3g457dga300gb92261d40921": ["<i>Observe the pair for any signs of injury.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "52aa8fbb-90dd-7294-7b07-81c1ff53490e"], "hf927c9a4g786cg44dcgb66cgd78dee4d0277": ["*Nothing. Both animals look fine, watching you expectantly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "91cadf63-9d30-d015-6c54-787f1c133bbc"], "h36e78db9g2347g4ae7g93b2g5b8d87486e62": ["<i>Hold Scratch's gaze and incline your head towards the cub - everything all right?</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "89942823-e218-0752-4cfa-f6239e82396e"], "h43581a99gea0bg47edga280gef8d2df9ded7": ["*Scratch's tail wags furiously. These two have become firm friends.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "110f4fd5-9584-2824-15ef-4953e74fd51f"], "h552ff852g1e44g49f7ga925gca8f9967615a": ["*Scratch looks at you in confusion. His tail wags enthusiastically, nonetheless.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "166506b6-b1a1-bb47-043d-63f2e2e0f358"], "h2667e212g0e47g4f80g9a43geee81ca66d03": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "1117f388-5ac6-0198-6e66-0a3418840ced"], "h2f82d902g8de5g42dfg83dag46e912376259": ["<i>Observe the pair for any signs of injury.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "dafbf14f-9bcc-f38c-ba3f-d58af35a778f"], "hfe8c9a14g9373g41a6g9b91g46f9a4d80113": ["*Nothing. Both animals look fine.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "fe4c19ca-e08e-d9ec-a401-868727282608"], "h09a1114age0b3g4a5dg8539g365d68a0d1ba": ["<i>Leave it. Those animals aren't your concern.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "348f5302-0070-3e3e-607e-2685a1aca722"], "h87259d05g5d23g49d2g8e3ageb6f6d46dbf3": ["*The sounds stop. Whatever just happened, it's too late to intervene now.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "5c28303f-808f-b54b-3d93-46f7eab09ff5"], "h369965cagef4fg494dg89ecg3065e3fc3490": ["<i>Call out for the owlbear cub.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "d797922c-deb7-0e5b-6509-3296990a1cbe"], "h19238958ge491g4a2cg8be8g81f548b8fc7a": ["*No response. The cub doesn't even have a name for you to shout out.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "4ee5d76b-f19e-d4e9-3693-60aa921de2cf"], "ha063103bg32b7g4249gb399ge1ac2f96e344": ["<i>Forget it - they'll turn up.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "e1fe6bb0-f0b0-ecc4-a438-97193ee3bfa8"], "h9b386f50g4c5dg49b8g9450g2c01fba6a79a": ["<i>Ignore it. The dog'll turn up.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog.html", "2684c9e7-28b8-b34e-d0c7-cac6a4eb512a"]}